result.execSummary:
The defendant Alexander L Stockland was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Alexander L Stockland is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Alexander L Stockland was found guilty of Possession of THC [Modifiers: PTAC, as a Party to a Crime], an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(e).
